<%
  const pillClass = "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-horriver-border bg-white/[0.04] px-3 py-2 text-[11px] leading-none text-horriver-light";
  const statCardClass = "rounded-[1.35rem] border border-horriver-border bg-white/[0.04] px-4 py-4 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.04)]";
  const statCardAccentClass = "rounded-[1.35rem] border border-horriver-orange/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-horriver-orange/12 via-black/35 to-black/60 px-4 py-4 shadow-[0_14px_36px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)]";
  const eyebrowClass = "inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-horriver-orange/20 bg-horriver-orange/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#ffb685]";
%>

<section class="space-y-7 animate-fadeIn">
  <header class="page-hero text-center space-y-4">
    <span class="hero-badge text-horriver-gray mx-auto">
      <span class="hero-icon">SB</span>
      Sobre
    </span>
    <h1 class="font-title text-4xl md:text-5xl text-horriver-light">
      Sobre o Horriver Plate
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-horriver-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Onde o futebol raiz encontra amizade, estatisticas e a resenha de terca-feira a noite.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
      <span class="<%= pillClass %>"><strong class="text-horriver-orange font-semibold">Pelada</strong> organizada</span>
      <span class="<%= pillClass %>"><strong class="text-horriver-orange font-semibold">Stats</strong> registradas</span>
      <span class="<%= pillClass %>"><strong class="text-horriver-orange font-semibold">Resenha</strong> eternizada</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-[220px,1fr] gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="page-section">
      <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg flex justify-center">
        <img
          src="/img/logo.jpg"
          alt="Escudo Horriver Plate"
          class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,122,26,0.4)]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <article class="page-section">
      <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg space-y-5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          O <span class="text-horriver-orange font-semibold">Horriver Plate</span> nasceu de um grupo de amigos apaixonados
          por futebol e resenha. Toda terca-feira, os craques e os bagres se reunem para jogar, rir,
          discutir os lances e criar historias que viram lenda.
        </p>

        <p>
          Aqui a competitividade existe, mas o espirito continua leve. Cada gol, assistencia, defesa e
          ate aquele chute isolado entram para a memoria da pelada e fazem parte da tradicao do grupo.
        </p>

        <p>
          O site surgiu para organizar tudo isso com cara de produto de verdade: gols, presencas, notas,
          fotos, rankings e destaques da temporada, sem perder a identidade de futebol raiz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="page-section">
      <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg space-y-3">
        <span class="<%= eyebrowClass %>">Essencia</span>
        <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-horriver-light">Futebol raiz</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-horriver-gray leading-relaxed">
          A base do projeto e simples: bola rolando, amizade forte e competitividade na medida certa.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-section">
      <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg space-y-3">
        <span class="<%= eyebrowClass %>">Produto</span>
        <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-horriver-light">Memoria da pelada</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-horriver-gray leading-relaxed">
          O que antes ficava so na conversa agora vira historico: artilharia, notas, fotos, premios e recordes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-section">
      <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg space-y-3">
        <span class="<%= eyebrowClass %>">Visao</span>
        <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-horriver-light">Cara de clube</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-horriver-gray leading-relaxed">
          A ideia e tratar a resenha com capricho visual e estatistico, como se a pelada fosse um clube grande.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="page-section__inner page-section__inner--lg">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-horriver-light">O que voce encontra aqui</h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-horriver-gray/80">Uma visao completa da vida do Horriver dentro e fora da quadra.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <article class="<%= statCardAccentClass %>">
          <span class="block text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-horriver-gray/90">Rankings</span>
          <strong class="mt-3 block text-[clamp(1.4rem,2vw,2rem)] leading-none text-horriver-orange font-semibold">01</strong>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-horriver-light/90">gols, assistencias, notas, fotos e overall</span>
        </article>
        <article class="<%= statCardClass %>">
          <span class="block text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-horriver-gray/90">Peladas</span>
          <strong class="mt-3 block text-[clamp(1.4rem,2vw,2rem)] leading-none text-horriver-light font-semibold">02</strong>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-horriver-gray">historico das partidas com estatisticas organizadas</span>
        </article>
        <article class="<%= statCardClass %>">
          <span class="block text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-horriver-gray/90">Elenco</span>
          <strong class="mt-3 block text-[clamp(1.4rem,2vw,2rem)] leading-none text-horriver-light font-semibold">03</strong>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-horriver-gray">perfil de jogador, conquistas e fase recente</span>
        </article>
        <article class="<%= statCardClass %>">
          <span class="block text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-horriver-gray/90">Destaques</span>
          <strong class="mt-3 block text-[clamp(1.4rem,2vw,2rem)] leading-none text-horriver-light font-semibold">04</strong>
          <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-horriver-gray">hall da fama, craques e premiacoes da temporada</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="text-center text-[12px] text-horriver-gray/80 mt-2">
    <p>
      Projeto idealizado e mantido por
      <span class="text-horriver-orange font-semibold">Gabriel Castro</span>
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center mt-4">
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/_hpfrc/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-horriver-orange/50 bg-black/30 text-horriver-orange hover:bg-horriver-orange hover:text-black transition-colors text-sm"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5">
          <path d="M7.75 2C4.678 2 2 4.678 2 7.75v8.5C2 19.322 4.678 22 7.75 22h8.5c3.072 0 5.75-2.678 5.75-5.75v-8.5C22 4.678 19.322 2 16.25 2h-8.5zM12 7.25a4.75 4.75 0 1 1 0 9.5a4.75 4.75 0 0 1 0-9.5zm0 1.5a3.25 3.25 0 1 0 0 6.5a3.25 3.25 0 0 0 0-6.5zm5.25-.75a.75.75 0 1 1 0-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5z"/>
        </svg>
        @_hpfrc
      </a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</section>
